   Usage: aai claude install [OPTIONS]
  
   Install the AssemblyAI docs MCP server and skill into Claude Code.
  
  ╭─ Options ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
  │ --scope        TEXT  Config scope to register the MCP under: user, project,  │
  │                      or local. Presence is detected across all scopes.       │
  │                      [default: user]                                         │
  │ --force              Reinstall even if already present.                      │
  │ --json               Output raw JSON.                                        │
  │ --help               Show this message and exit.                             │
  ╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
  
   Examples
   Wire AssemblyAI docs + skill into Claude Code
   $ aai claude install
   Install for the current project only
   $ aai claude install --scope project
  
  
  
  '''
